title: 插件启动问题
txt_content:
登陆插件:AuthMe  在 控制台发出的
[AuthMe] WARNING! The protectInventory feature requires ProtocolLib! Disabling it...

控制台 里出现的   没有标明是那个插件    
[11:09:46 WARN]: **** SERVER IS RUNNING IN OFFLINE/INSECURE MODE!
[11:09:46 WARN]: The server will make no attempt to authenticate usernames. Beware.
[11:09:46 WARN]: While this makes the game possible to play without internet access, it also opens up the ability for hackers to connect with any username they choose.
[11:09:46 WARN]: To change this, set "online-mode" to "true" in the server.properties file.


可以调试吗？

replies.author: s8566597s
replies.txt_content:
又是你
authme有个protectInventory功能需要前置插件ProtocolLib，你可以在设置里关闭它
这个功能是在玩家登陆之前看不到物品栏里的东西
另外下面那个提示信息是说你的服务器关了验证模式，盗版也能进的意思
